%25AB%2598%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25BA%259D%25E6%25B7%25A1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258E%25BB-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF&h=f1a46827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170503/2_506714_0/-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%80%9A%E7%B7%9D-%E9%83%AD%E6%96%87%E8%B2%B4%E8%A6%AA%E5%8F%A3%E7%88%86%E7%8C%9B%E6%96%992-%E6%B5%B7%E8%88%AA%E9%AB%98%E5%83%B9%E8%B2%B7%E5%9C%B0%E6%BA%9D%E6%B7%A1%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E6%B4%BE%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E9%81%8E%E5%8E%BB-%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF</a><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪好多人同我一樣 早就估到呢D陰毛論<br />\n只係大家一直收埋冇討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢幾年黎 香港發生好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都係D hints<br />\n好似一直鋪緊路 掌握緊香港既未來咁<br />\n<br />\n以下係一D事件同睇法...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 銅書店事件  (做到殺雞儆猴 書商睇到出所謂內地&quot;禁書&quot;咁大件事 好多都唔夠膽出 自然作者都唔敢寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n2. 內地發展商係香港大量投地/囤地 再派大班人大量買樓 以致減少供應 推高樓價(呢個郭文貴有講 當有人拎住大把錢 做到港地/樓市壟斷 香港人大半生所賺既錢 最終都係流入中央 要做到樓市下跌都唔係冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  eg令到香港爆發新致命疾病 大鵬灣核電如果出事港樓都玩完 到事供樓供到一半既港人就真係卡左係度)<br />\n<br />\n3. 食物污染 (避孕藥、類荷爾蒙)--&gt; 令香港人生育減少/生女多 (令香港女多男少 長遠黎講 陸男黎香港入侵搵女人發展定居更易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n4. 推行國民教育 (思想教育)<br />\n<br />\n5. 2011係大帽山雷射站 附近起左個軍事雷達 比解放軍使用<br />\n(接受香港情報 方便公安做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140720/18806156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20140720%2F18806156&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2AuywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a5c0997d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20140720%2F18806156&h=a21b1ee4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20140720/18806156</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得上面所講既o岩唔o岩<br />\n會唔會有其他睇法<br />\n不過講左咁多 我地所知既 好多時都係由傳媒提供<br />\n過多30年之後 所有新聞好可能都和諧哂 到時講都冇得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa009c5dd85fc90a56de1c061e0adeba2c08a7a","tid":228253,"uid":106422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T18:02:56.000Z","msg":"以前高登都講左好多年啦"},{"pid":"191200acd6fb014db0c51bc67906bc8a026cbf8f","tid":228253,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}